<h3>Introduction</h3>
<p>We believe that information-gathering and use should go hand-in-hand with transparency. This Privacy Policy explains how <%= COMPLIANCE_COMPANY[:company_name] %>, the organization that hosts this site, collects, uses, and shares information we receive from you through your use of this site. It is essential to understand that, by using this site, you consent to the collection, transfer, processing, storage, disclosure, and use of your information as described in this Privacy Policy. That means that reading this Policy carefully is important.</p>
<p>We do not sell or rent your Personal Information, nor do we give it to others to sell you anything. We use it to process your Verified Consumer Request and deliver that request to the business that you designate. We also use your behavior on this site to improve the usability and features that are offered.</p>
<hr />
